{
  "stem": "3638.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My opinion is, he's entitled to that money, because he, he protect us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Put it this way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Where everybody was starving and, and, and, and dying in Plaszow, we were sitting over there, and, and we live like, like nothing, like a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was able-- He was able to make himself money on the side, and he used to come-- there was strict guidelines.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The factory had to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was working seven days a week, day and night, working day and night, or shift, and, and he was producing the pots and pans for the military and for the other things, and he was living very well.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He used to come with a-- with a Mercedes car every day dressed in different suit, and sometimes three times a day.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he had girlfriends, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had a good life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we didn't have a bad life, either, because of that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe he change it after he saw what's happening in the, in the Cracow ghetto, and, and maybe-- he was a very shrewd man-- and maybe he saw as a ticket to live after the war, because he knew it.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because that was the time when Stalingrad fell, and we got the news.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Stalingrad fell, and Odessa fell.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he knew that the German are going bad, so he want to create a good will.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that's what he did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is my opinion.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're saying there might have been some ulterior motives?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ulterior motives, but at the same time, he, he was not bad, and he had-- and he was always-- and he, he was looking after Bankier.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I still say Bankier was the most important man for him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was horrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
